                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <div class="thumbnail">
                        <img src="<%= asset_path 'web-crawler.png' %>" alt="New York" width="400" height="300">
                        <p><strong>웹 크롤러</strong></p>
                        <p>- Data Crawling</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <div class="thumbnail">
                        <img src="<%= asset_path 'application-software.png' %>" alt="San Francisco" width="400" height="300">
                        <p><strong>응용 소프트웨어</strong></p>
                        <p>- App</p>
                        <p>- Web</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    <!-- Container (Main Things Section) 3 -->
        <div class="col-sm-12 container-fluid">
            <div class="row portfolio-list">
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <div class="thumbnail">
                        <a href="/portfolio/web/bebeliebe">
                            <img src="<%= asset_path 'web/main/web-1.png' %>" alt="web-1.png">
                            <div class="overlay"><i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i></div>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <div class="thumbnail">
                        <a href="/portfolio/logo/joynco">
                            <img src="<%= asset_path 'logo/main/logo-5.png' %>" alt="logo-5.png">
                            <div class="overlay"><i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i></div>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <div class="thumbnail">
                        <a href="/portfolio/web/joynco">
                            <img src="<%= asset_path 'web/main/web-2.png' %>" alt="web-2.png">
                            <div class="overlay"><i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i></div>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <div class="thumbnail">
                        <a href="/portfolio/logo/multimediacurpos">
                            <img src="<%= asset_path 'logo/main/logo-4.png' %>" alt="logo-4.png">
                            <div class="overlay"><i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i></div>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <div class="thumbnail">
                        <a href="/portfolio/web/multimediacurpos">
                            <img src="<%= asset_path 'web/main/web-3.png' %>" alt="web-3.png">
                            <div class="overlay"><i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i></div>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <div class="thumbnail">
                        <a href="/portfolio/logo/meetu">
                            <img src="<%= asset_path 'logo/main/logo-6.png' %>" alt="logo-6.png">
                            <div class="overlay"><i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i></div>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row more-link">
                <div class="col-sm-12">
                    <a class="col-sm-12 btn btn-default btn-lg" href='portfolio/portfolio'>VIEW ALL</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    <!-- Container (Company About Section) 4 -->
        <div class="col-sm-12 container-fluid">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-3"><strong>Caramella Inc.</strong></div>
                <div class="col-sm-9">
                    <div>
                        카라멜라는 소프트웨어와 디자인을 만드는 회사입니다. <br />
                        우리는 젊고 트렌디한 감성으로 시대의 감각을 반영하는 디자인과 
                        사용자가 편리하게 이용할 수 있는 소프트웨어를 만들어 
                        고객과 소비자 접점에 서서 가장 효율적이고 창의적인 아이디어를 도출해 내어
                        최고의 성과를 낼 수있는 Post human을 지향하고 있습니다. <br />
                        우리는 항상 남들과 다르게 접근을 하며 특별한 아이디어로 고객과 소통합니다.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    <!-- Container (Public Relation Section) 5 -->
        <div class="col-sm-12 container-fluid">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-12"><h2>Public Relation</h2></div>
                <div id="myCarousel" class="col-sm-12 carousel slide text-center" data-ride="carousel">
                <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
                    <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
                    <% @prs.each do |pr| %>
                        <div class="item">
                            <h4><%= link_to pr.title, pr %></h4>
                        </div>
                    <% end %>
                        <script>   
                            $(document).on('ready', function() {
                                $(".carousel-inner .item:nth-child(1)").addClass('active');
                            });
                        </script>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Left and right controls -->
                    <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                    </a>
                    <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
